		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#aa2252" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#aa2252">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/drdata2.assets/Image_19.png')" x="64" y="128" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士凝聚「拟像·祸津御建鸣神命」，使用恶曜太刀短时蓄力后立即下劈，造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害并向两侧挤开玩家。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/drdata2.assets/Image_20.png')" x="1392" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="439" height="85" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士在场地四边放置4枚激光器，产生激光束并向对面进行移动，到终点消失，接触激光束持续造成<span color="#b8b8b8">35%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="56" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士在玩家身旁四个位置产生方形脉冲波，均造成<span color="#b8b8b8">35%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="56" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士立即摆臂，产生3股黑潮浅浪，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">45%</span><span>伤害。仅入场施放一次。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="425" height="143" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士立即移至边缘，并展开<span textDecoration="underline">壁障</span><span>，同时全抗性</span><span color="#ffdfbf">+300%</span><span>；35s后施放「万有成灰此世无」。壁障每隔6s将玩家猛地推向另一侧，钻入壁障上的缺口可避免被推走，一共有3种孔型。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="991" width="438" height="114" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士将利用世界树的能力，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">150%</span><span>伤害同时</span><span color="#ffbfbf">秒杀</span><span>前台角色。壁障击破后，博士将拥有</span><span textDecoration="underline">蓄能进度</span><span>，进度归零后中断蓄力，并瘫痪12s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/drdata2.assets/Image_21.png')" x="719" y="393">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/drdata2.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1392" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
