		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="431" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">博士凝聚「拟像·修库特尔」，并向前依次斩出火刀域霜刀剑气，依次造成<span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>,</span><span color="#99ffff">80%</span><span>伤害，随后发射密集弹幕，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">35%</span><span>伤害，部分子弹造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害。<br/>伤害均带有(1,0.6,0.3,0.1)的衰减。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
